a-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Facilities &amp; Features</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">1<!-- --> <!-- -->answer</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">1</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Rules &amp; Etiquette</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Events &amp; Parties</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button><button type=\"button\" aria-pressed=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-btn \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-name\">Training</span><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-preview\">0<!-- --> <!-- -->answers</span></div><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-count\">0</span></button></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a sidebar-card support-card\"><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a support-label\">Still stuck?</p><h3 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Chat with our team</h3><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Share your situation and we&#x27;ll recommend the best park, indoor option, or community meetup.</p><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a support-actions\"><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Contact us</a><a href=\"/signup\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a secondary\">Join community</a></div></div></aside><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-main\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-rail\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-eyebrow\">Popular right now</span><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Tap to jump to the full answer.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-chip-row\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a popular-chip\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-question-circle\"></i>Can I take my dog to the Great Smoky Mountains?</button></div></div><div role=\"list\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-accordion\"><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">01</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Can I take my dog to the Great Smoky Mountains?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">Dogs are permitted on only two trails in Great Smoky Mountains National Park: the Gatlinburg Trail and Oconaluftee River Trail.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">Planning Your Visit</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Dogs are permitted on only two trails in Great Smoky Mountains National Park: the Gatlinburg Trail and Oconaluftee River Trail. Leashes required at all times. Most visitors explore adjacent national forest land which has more permissive policies.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->Planning Your Visit</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article><article role=\"listitem\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-row \"><button type=\"button\" aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger\"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-main\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-index\">02</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><h4 class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">What is Shelby Farms Park like for dogs?</h4><p class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-preview\">Shelby Farms in Memphis offers over 200 acres of off-leash space with varied terrain including fields, woods, and lake access.</p></div></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-trigger-meta\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a category-chip\">Facilities &amp; Features</span><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-chevron-down\"></i></div></button><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel \"><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-answer\"><p style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;line-height:1.7\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Shelby Farms in Memphis offers over 200 acres of off-leash space with varied terrain including fields, woods, and lake access. It&#x27;s one of the largest urban dog parks in America.</p></div><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a faq-panel-actions\"><span class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\">Category · <!-- -->Facilities &amp; Features</span><div class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a panel-buttons\"><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-hand-thumbs-up\"></i> Helpful</button><button type=\"button\" class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a\"><i class=\"jsx-ef56c8b56212c77a bi bi-share\"></i> Share</button></div></div></div></article></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"state-section alt\"><div class=\"section-shell\"><div class=\"cta-band\"><div><h3>